api_analysis_prompt.user_prompt_template:
Analyze the following API documentation and extract key details for creating an MCP tool.

API DOCUMENTATION:
{api_documentation}

Please provide a JSON response with the following structure:
{{
    "api_name": "Clear, descriptive name for the API",
    "description": "Brief description of what this API does",
    "base_url": "Base URL if identifiable",
    "endpoints": [
        {{
            "path": "/path/to/endpoint",
            "method": "GET/POST/etc",
            "description": "What this endpoint does"
        }}
    ],
    "parameters": {{
        "param_name": {{
            "type": "string/integer/boolean/etc",
            "description": "Parameter description",
            "required": true/false,
            "default": "default_value_if_any"
        }}
    }},
    "authentication": {{
        "type": "api_key/bearer/basic/oauth",
        "location": "header/query/body",
        "parameter_name": "name_of_auth_parameter"
    }},
    "response_format": {{
        "type": "json/xml/text",
        "structure": "Description of response structure"
    }},
    "usage_examples": [
        "Example usage patterns or code snippets"
    ]
}}

Focus on extracting practical information needed to create a working tool. If some information is not available, use reasonable defaults or mark as null.
Respond with ONLY the JSON, no additional text.
